project:        dclm-staff




## setup
- install scoop (windows)
ref: https://scoop.sh/
+
Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser
irm get.scoop.sh | iex
scoop --version
+
- install nodejs, nvm
scoop install nodejs nvm
+
-  get yarn
scoop install yarn
+
- set nodejs version
nvm install 8.11.2
nvm use 8.11.2
node -v
npm -v